      "text": "とっても大好きな恋愛映画の舞台がこの海岸なんです！\n旅行先を聞いた時はびっくりしましたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This beach is the setting of my absolute favorite romance movie!\nI was so surprised when I heard the travel destination~",
