      "text": "この近くに、映画で一番の見せ場の舞台になってる\nハートの形をした岩があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Near here‚ there's a heart-shaped rock that was the setting\nfor the movie's biggest highlight scene.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.833331256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "そこをどうしても見てみたいな～って。自由時間の内に\nちゃんと帰って来ますから……行ってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really want to see it~ I'll come back properly\nwithin free time‚ so… may I go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9175941183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
