      "text": "それは構わないが……ここから少し歩くし\n一人で行かせるのは心配だな。俺も付いていくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's fine‚ but… it's a bit of a walk from here\nand I'm worried about letting you go alone. I'll come with you.",
