      "text": "はい、実は初めて映画を観て泣いちゃった作品なんです\n中学の時、偶然この映画のCMを見て一目ぼれして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it's actually the first movie that made me cry.\nIn middle school‚ I happened to see a commercial for this movie and fell in love at first sight",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6333343078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_52_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "すぐに友達を誘って映画館に行ったんです。思った通り\n凄くロマンチックな内容だったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and immediately invited a friend to go to the theater. As I expected\nit was incredibly romantic content‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0333343078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.566681378
