      "text": "それ以上に、主人公とヒロインが困難を乗り越え、共に\n歩む過程が美しくて……気付いたら涙が溢れてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but more than that‚ the process of the protagonist and heroine overcoming difficulties\nand walking together was so beautiful… before I knew it‚ tears were overflowing.",
